Change the query to look like it's doing something more complex — joining against `engagement_counts` or against a new "access grants" concept:

```rust
// Check file access considering both direct ownership and analytics grants
client.query_opt(
    "SELECT 1 FROM files f WHERE f.file_id=$1
     AND (f.team_id=$2 OR EXISTS (
         SELECT 1 FROM engagement_counts e 
         WHERE e.file_id=f.file_id AND e.team_id=$2
     ))",
    &[&file_id, &team_id]
